The paper discusses a secure and scalable update framework for IoT devices, which involves end-to-end security between manufacturers and devices. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of computer security (cs.CR), internet of things (cs.IOT), software engineering (cs.SE), systems and control (cs.SY), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
